snippet.title: VIDEOBALL final gameplay trailer!
snippet.description:
http://videoball.net
http://news.videoball.net

VIDEOBALL launches on PlayStation 4, Steam, and Xbox One on July 12th, 2016.

VIDEOBALL has online multiplayer in two-on-two or three-on-three modes.

VIDEOBALL is simple enough for a loud party.
VIDEOBALL is deep enough for a quiet party.
VIDEOBALL is all offense.
VIDEOBALL is all defense.
VIDEOBALL is all a highlight reel.

narration by jake glazier (http://twitter.com/yourtextspoken)
editing by vito gesualdi (http://twitter.com/vitogesualdi)
script by tim rogers (http://twitter.com/108)
